title: Resume Builder Pro v1.61
description:
Resume Builder Pro is the top-rated resume maker in the Play Store! It manages the important details of your resume and allows you to generate a DOCX (Microsoft Word) file instantly. 

The DOCX file is sent to your e-mail for your convenience. You can also download it to your phone and send it directly to potential employers.

Never worry about starting from scratch again because Resume Builder Pro makes it easy to update your resume to reflect your most current information.

Resume categories include:

- Contact Information
- Objective
- Experience
- Education
- Skills
- References

What's New:

(v1.61) New ability to send the resume as an attachment in an e-mail. Upgraded resume backend - resumes are now created in less than 10 seconds.
(v1.53) Helper text, improved UI. Fixed UTF-8 encoding issue.
(v1.50) Improved UI. Zip codes can now contain both numbers and letters.
(v1.32) Upgraded resume generator to provide a more modern file format (DOCX).
